<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">预计，华北、黄淮等地的强对流天气主要影响时段为今天午后至夜间。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>全</span></strong><strong><span>文434字</span></strong><strong><span>，阅读约</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>需2分钟 </span></strong></span></p>
